node.text: Kit & Krysta play #NewPokemonSnap from the very beginning and show the opening areas. Which Pokémon are you excited to photograph when the game launches on April 30? #NintendoMinute

On this day in 2008, The World Ends With You debuted on #NintendoDS in North America! What are your favorite memories of this @SquareEnix classic?
 
The Reapers’ Game begins once more in the long-awaited sequel: NEO: The World Ends With You, launching for #NintendoSwitch on 7/27! #TWEWY #NTWEWY
Who is your favorite Asterisk holder in #BravelyDefault II and why is it Dag Rampage?

It's LEGO Luigi time! Introducing the #LEGOSuperMario Adventures with Luigi Starter Course! Discover all the reactions of LEGO Luigi as he jumps through your levels, meets up with Pink Yoshi, and goes face-to-face with Boom Boom. Pre-order today! 

#LEGO #SuperMario #Luigi #Nintendo

It’s prom night in #AnimalCrossing: New Horizons! Special guests @kungfufruitcup and @stephen_georg join Kit & Krysta to share some of their real life prom memories.

Share your favorite prom memories with us in the comments!
Check out a fresh selection of indie games coming to #NintendoSwitch from some of our indie partners from around the world in the latest #IndieWorld Showcase!

Today marks the 20th anniversary of the #AnimalCrossing series! What are your favorite memories? Thank you to everyone who has played throughout the years, and we look forward to sharing more memories together in the future!
A new #IndieWorld Showcase arrives on Wednesday, April 14 at 9 a.m. PT! Tune in for a livestream featuring roughly 20 minutes focused on fresh and new indie games coming to #NintendoSwitch.
Introducing a fresh new blue color #NintendoSwitchLite, launching on 5/21 for $199.99. The blue Nintendo Switch Lite will release separately on the same day as the hilarious adventure game, #Miitopia
Can you guess the Pokémon? Play along with Kit & Krysta on this episode of #NintendoMinute! #NewPokemonSnap
Looks like we’re not the only ones with #MonsterHunterRise on the brain! Check out @likovacs’ DIY take on the Kamura Palamute set and @missgandakris’ homemade Khezu Palico set!

WAKA WAKA WAKA! 🟡🟡🟡

Test your chomping chops in a 99-player PAC-Royale! PAC-MAN™ 99 is available to download now, exclusively for #NintendoSwitchOnline members. #PACMAN99
PAC-MAN™ is back in a new 99-PAC-MAN battle royale! PAC-MAN™ 99 goes live 4/7 at 6 PM PST, exclusively for #NintendoSwitchOnline members! #PACMAN99 🟡🟡🟡
Time for tea with the 4 Heroes of Light from #BravelyDefault II! ☕ Looks way better than silverfish!
Get ready for the #AnimalCrossing: New Horizons collection from @buildabear, launching tomorrow! Sign up for email updates on the Build-A-Bear website to find out when the collection is available.
Hop into the holiday festivities with some egg-citing adventures! What game are you playing today?
Kit & Krysta are joined by special guests @_missclick_ and PlayerEssence to hunt the Bishaten in Monster Hunter Rise on today’s episode of Nintendo Minute! #MHRise @capcomusa @monsterhuntergame
An Apple a Day keeps the Appling at bay! 🍎 Enjoy a snack with the heroes of #BravelyDefault II!

Revel in the spring season with discoveries coming to your island in the month of April! Enjoy the beauty of Cherry blossoms in full bloom at the start of the month, or plan your own prom with seasonal items and outfits to buy! We hope you continue enjoying life on your island in #AnimalCrossing: New Horizons. #ACNH
In this latest Six Quick Things video, Capcom’s Yuri Araujo walks us through some of #MonsterHunterRise’s new additions, including powerful pups and poisoned persimmons!
Thank you to everyone who joined us in commemorating the 35th anniversary of Super Mario Bros. We hope you continue to Power-Up and enjoy Mario and friends’ adventures! #SuperMario35
See a full hunt from start to finish in Monster Hunter Rise on the latest #NintendoMinute! @monsterhuntergame @capcomusa #MHRise

What would it be like to have a more fun walking experience surrounded by #Pikmin? In a new mobile app developed by Niantic and Nintendo coming later in 2021, explore the real world and create memories with your Pikmin friends.
Happy first anniversary, #AnimalCrossing: New Horizons! What’s been your favorite island memory so far? #ACNH

Kit & Krysta are unboxing the Monster Hunter Rise Collector’s Edition on this week’s episode of #NintendoMinute. Be sure to stay until the end to see an amiibo size comparison! @capcomusa @monsterhuntergame
